Documentation workflow for Shahnameh TD:

- **Index:** [docs/DOC_INDEX.md](docs/DOC_INDEX.md) — start here for reading order.
- **Design canon:** README_00 through README_05 (from repo PDFs). Do not contradict locked decisions in README_00 without explicit user approval.
- **Implementation truth:** [GODOT_PORT_STATUS.md](docs/GODOT_PORT_STATUS.md) and [IMPLEMENTATION_STATUS.md](docs/IMPLEMENTATION_STATUS.md) — label “design target” vs “built today”; do not mark aspirational PDF features as shipped.
- **Godot-first:** test instructions use F5/F6 in `shahname-td-godot/shahname-td/`, not Unity menus.
- **Khan 1 gate:** first production target is one map until voluntary replay is proven.
- **Monetization docs:** follow README_03 — cosmetics-first launch; IAP/subscription stubs in code are deferred.
- **Unity docs** (`UNITY_ARCHITECTURE.md`, `UNITY_SETUP.md`): archived pointers only.

When syncing from PDFs, prefer updating README_XX files then linking specialized docs (`GAME_HANDOFF`, `PRD`, etc.) rather than duplicating full prompt inventories.
